    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and stock dampening rates, preserving the original suspension geometry and communicative steering rack feedback. A driver-grade specimen optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
