    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW M3 finished in Mineral Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a joy to own and is in solid condition both mechanically and aesthetically. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel consistent with regular use. Inside, the Black Merino leather seats are firm and comfortable; the driver's side bolster shows light wear from entry, but the cabin remains free of smoke or pet odors. All interior technology, including the premium Harman Kardon surround sound and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the S55 twin-turbo engine runs flawlessly, backed by a complete service history and a recent inspection that confirmed no leaks or pending issues. The car sits on Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with approximately 60% tread life remaining. This is a turn-key performance sedan ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
